    <name>
      <text>Creating histograms and frequency polygon for time spent on social media</text>
    </name>
    <questiontext format="moodle_auto_format">
      <text><![CDATA[<p>
A survey was conducted to find out how much time people spend on social media daily.
</p>

<table border="1" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0">
<tr>
  <th>Time (minutes)</th>
  <th>Frequency</th>
  <th>Class width</th>
  <th>Midpoint</th>
  <th>Frequency density</th>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td>0–10</td>
  <td>{@freq[1]@}</td>
  <td>{@widths[1]@}</td>
  <td>[[input:m1]] [[validation:m1]][[feedback:prt_m1]]</td>
  <td>[[input:d1]] [[validation:d1]][[feedback:prt1]]</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td>10–20</td>
  <td>{@freq[2]@}</td>
  <td>{@widths[2]@}</td>
  <td>[[input:m2]] [[validation:m2]][[feedback:prt_m2]]</td>
  <td>[[input:d2]] [[validation:d2]][[feedback:prt2]]</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td>20–30</td>
  <td>{@freq[3]@}</td>
  <td>{@widths[3]@}</td>
  <td>[[input:m3]] [[validation:m3]][[feedback:prt_m3]]</td>
  <td>[[input:d3]] [[validation:d3]][[feedback:prt3]]</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td>30–60</td>
  <td>{@freq[4]@}</td>
  <td>{@widths[4]@}</td>
  <td>[[input:m4]] [[validation:m4]][[feedback:prt_m4]]</td>
  <td>[[input:d4]] [[validation:d4]][[feedback:prt4]]</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td>60–120</td>
  <td>{@freq[5]@}</td>
  <td>{@widths[5]@}</td>
  <td>[[input:m5]] [[validation:m5]][[feedback:prt_m5]]</td>
  <td>[[input:d5]] [[validation:d5]][[feedback:prt5]]</td>
</tr>
</table>

<p>
Once you have calculated the frequency densities, adjust the points on the graph so that
the histogram and frequency polygon are correct.
</p>
[[jsxgraph]]
var board = JXG.JSXGraph.initBoard(divid, {
    boundingbox: [-5, 8, 130, -1],
    axis: true,
    showCopyright: false
});

/* Data from STACK */
var lower = [0,10,20,30,60];
var upper = [10,20,30,60,120];
var mids  = [{#midpoints[1]#},{#midpoints[2]#},{#midpoints[3]#},{#midpoints[4]#},{#midpoints[5]#}];

/* True densities */
var dens = [{#densities[1]#},{#densities[2]#},{#densities[3]#},{#densities[4]#},{#densities[5]#}];

/* Draw histogram rectangles */
for (let i=0; i<5; i++) {
  board.create('polygon', [
    [lower[i],0],
    [upper[i],0],
    [upper[i],dens[i]],
    [lower[i],dens[i]]
  ], {
    fillOpacity: 0.2,
    withLines: false
  });
}

/* Draggable frequency polygon points */
var pts = [];
for (let i=0; i<5; i++) {
  pts.push(
    board.create('point', [mids[i], 1], {
      name: '',
      size: 3
    })
  );
}

/* Connect points */
board.create('polygonalchain', pts);
[[/jsxgraph]]]]></text>
